descript.abstract: Outline and location of edge of road. Subtypes used to indicate; Edge of Pavement, Edge of Dirt, Back of Curb and Edge of Alley.
descript.purpose: The purpose of this data set is to show outline and location of edge of road. Subtypes used to indicate; Edge of Pavement, Edge of Dirt, Back of Curb and Edge of Alley.

idinfo.accconst: Users of this data agree to the use constraints described in this metadata document.
idinfo.useconst: Pursuant to Section 54.1-402, paragraph C of the Code of Virginia, which is quoted below, this data may not be used for purposes listed in said paragraph C, since the data was not created, nor is it maintained under the supervision of a licensed land surveyor.

citeinfo.origin: City of Lynchburg Department of GIS

procstep.procdesc: Original GIS vector data was being maintained in GeoMedia. The GIS vector was then exported to AutoCAD (.dwg) format and/or ESRI shapefile (.shp) format then loaded into ESRI Geodatabase format.

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.
